Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_analysis_precision_ps(25.10)        timing_analysis_precision_ps(25.10)

Name
       timing_analysis_precision_ps

Syntax
       timing_analysis_precision_ps

       {0.1 | 0.01}

       Default: 0.01 (in ps)

       Allows you to set the delay precision value for the write_sdf command.

       The  write_sdf  command  shows  a  double digit value after the decimal
       point by default. You can use this global variable for more accuracy.

       To set this global variable, you can use the set command.

